Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:05.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Where... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Are you the one who was calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.08,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Dammit... Not at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:00.46,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That was the day when I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:06.56,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:08.66,Default,Avrora,0,0,0,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:12.68,Default,Avrora,0,0,0,,Avrora Florestina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.04,Default,Avrora,0,0,0,,That is our name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:17.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Avrora...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:23.24,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Nine months ago, on my way back from visiting Nagisa in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:25.16,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.88,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The Twelfth Kaleid Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:29.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Avrora.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:36.62,Default,Avrora,0,0,0,,Kojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.98,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,And then {\i1}that{\i0} happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:46.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The event that caused me to awaken as the Fourth Primogenitor, and lose Avrora.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.56,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The Scorched Banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:55.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:56.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.88,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.46,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,It's fast! A therianthrope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:41.84,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,It got ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:42.78,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.80,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:46.60,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,642)}Just shut up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.28,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,What... the heck is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.30,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Mogwai, what's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.78,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,It's exactly as it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:01.36,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Demons all over Itogami Island collapsed all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.00,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,some monsters appeared, which are going wild after sucking their magical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.72,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Shit! How did this happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.08,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.82,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,The demon registration bracelets!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:16.66,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,A time-delayed virus has been inserted into the elementary magic circuit used for monitoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.32,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,You mean when the Island Guard got hacked yesterday!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.06,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,They got us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:27.82,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,The criminals weren't after the servers at headquarters, it was this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.10,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Can't you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.54,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,That would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.36,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,They've been cut off from the Island Guard network as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:38.66,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,And I have no physical means to apply a vaccine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.12,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Not quite. You have a way, don't you, Missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:47.14,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,A way to forcefully gain access to a demon registration bracelet that has been cut off from the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.30,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! It's "C"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:51.66,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.54,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,So that's why they're after you, Asagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.82,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.36,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.38,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Let's go to the Keystone Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.18,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.24,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,If you want to complain, I'll listen to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.90,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry... or Itogami Island might not exist after today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.54,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.74,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Oh, give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.86,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.50,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What's with the pathetic voice, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.74,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai! Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You were unconscious for close to an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,One hour... only that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.64,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I had a really long dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:41.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No... Avrora. That wasn't a dream, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.26,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.52,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,So you finally woke up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.70,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Mogwai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.46,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,You don't have the time to be lazing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.04,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Take a look at the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.46,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the heck is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Did Tartaros Lapus do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:05.30,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Yeah. They used a virus to hack into the demon registration bracelets and are gathering magical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Magical energy!? Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.02,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Look above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:11.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:14.04,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, that is a magic circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.44,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's so dense that I can scarcely believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So this is the true form of Tartaros' Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:29.26,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Asagi is currently on her way to the Keystone Gate to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:33.88,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Can you keep Itogami Island from falling to pieces in the meanwhile, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.78,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Falling to pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:36.82,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.50,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I won't let you do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out, Regulus-Aurum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.58,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,They resurrected!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.36,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,The summoning magic from that Rose is still in effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,In that case... Come out! Al-Meissa Mercury!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.18,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Thanks Himeragi! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.18,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I only did my job as your Observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.48,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But at this rate...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.58,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I know. The situation will only get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Dammit... What should I do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:47.84,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Der Freischutz!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:56.44,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,A magical bullet multi-lock on! This technique is... Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.56,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Kojou-kun! Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.66,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yuiri-san, Shio-san, and Kirasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.54,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Grenda, you came too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:07.70,Default,Grenda,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.72,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.14,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,So we just have to find the magician who is controlling that magic circle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.32,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.08,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,For a War Dancer, it's the most basic thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.50,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Boundary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:29.02,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,Authenticate! Freikugel Plus Proto III, unlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.06,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Rosenkavalier Plus! Boot up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:39.02,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Kojou-kun, leave this to us and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:46.70,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai. I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:51.54,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Himeragi? Why did you bring me all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.46,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's okay, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.46,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:01.78,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.64,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that it's okay to suck my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Don't make me say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:11.64,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Eh!? But why, all of a sudden!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,December-san's ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:17.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It seals your power to control Familiars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:26.76,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,If I'm not wrong, then increasing your vampiric power\Nwill allow you to keep ownership of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.64,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.54,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You don't want it to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.66,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I can't do that in this sort of situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.18,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,In that case, Senpai, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hmm? Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi... Is this your...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.58,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,My handkerchief wasn't long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So it's not your handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.56,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It smells kind of nice, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:13.16,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Smells like soap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.64,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Stop smelling it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I don't need your comments!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.00,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,H-Himeragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.28,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,How... is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,How should I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I want to keep doing this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:39.02,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No! It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.26,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,S-Senpai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Not there...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.44,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.48,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You musn't...! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, Senpai! Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.14,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You need to drink more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I can't do that, Himeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Your body can't take any more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:28.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But you might not be able to beat December-san the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.38,Default,Grenda,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.86,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,You can't, Grenda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.58,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yuiri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.12,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,It's not what you think, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.20,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Grenda was tired, so I wanted to let her rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:43.02,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,I wasn't peeking or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.36,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,K-Kojou-kun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.22,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Grenda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:54.94,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai. This is an emergency, so I'll allow it, just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.28,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Just this once, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.36,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Yuki... what do mean, "allow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.58,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Umm... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:04.72,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,I'm not against it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.24,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,This is my first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Bear with it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.36,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.82,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Yuki, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:30.38,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Koukarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.96,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,Kirasaka! How many shots do you have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.36,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Including my spares, six! How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.26,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.34,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,At this rate, we won't last more than three or four minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.56,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Hikawa Shio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.38,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Al-Nasl-Minium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.58,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:54.26,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,Akatsuki Kojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:55.84,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Sayaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.08,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late, Kirasaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.64,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Haba Yuiri... and Yukina, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.84,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Your faces are red, are you two okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.52,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.72,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Akatsuki Kojou! Don't tell me, you did it again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.92,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,The Four Heavenly Beasts!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:21.22,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,The mythical beasts said to govern over the four cardinal directions of heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.90,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,The symbols of power in Feng Shui...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:28.10,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... He used the structure of Itogami Island itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.74,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,which was built to correspond to the four gods!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So this is what Tartaros Lapus were really after!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.34,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,I've found the magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:41.06,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Direction, three o'clock, distance 6200 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:44.18,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,6200? Wouldn't that be on top of the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:47.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Itogami Island's abandoned District 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.16,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The former site of an early man-made island,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It was sunk only nine months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:55.74,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:14:01.38,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,If she's going to appear again one last time, that's the only place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:04.90,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Hikawa Shio?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.20,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.14,Default,Sayaka,0,0,0,,We'll buy you some time. Make it count!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.84,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Let's go, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:11.50,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.16,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Grenda, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.08,Default,Grenda,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.94,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Dammit, the Keystone Gate is right in front of our noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.56,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,There aren't any places left to hide and move anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.90,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,Need some help, Carly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.96,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,It's fine. I have them cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.88,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.42,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,I'll be the decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.54,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Run to the Keystone Gate as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:38.54,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.44,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,We don't have the time to hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.56,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Mogwai, I'll leave you to guide Asagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.38,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.38,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,I'm starting the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:51.76,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Three... Two... One... Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.90,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Oh no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.82,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,An Air Elemental!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.72,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,No, a Wraith!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:07.46,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,Something like that... If I destroy the clone, even the\Ntechnique user should receive damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.12,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,And now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.54,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:22.32,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,Sorry... December...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:26.34,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,I... In a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.04,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Dammit, I guess I tried too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.22,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,The rest is in your hands, Kojou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.18,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,Carly! What's wrong, Carly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Resistance is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Where is Senga Takehito?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.16,Default,Ran,0,0,0,,Program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:21.22,Default,Ran,0,0,0,,Tartaros Rose's network infiltration dropped to 77%.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:25.34,Default,Ran,0,0,0,,Demon registration bracelets... Signal lost from 4800 units.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.52,Default,December,0,0,0,,Even you can't stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,Aiba Asagi really is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,Ran, that's enough. Run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.20,Default,December,0,0,0,,I can handle the rest on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.30,Default,Ran,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.18,Default,Ran,0,0,0,,I don't... want to... go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.00,Default,December,0,0,0,,Stop it, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.42,Default,December,0,0,0,,She's a monster who has control over this entire man-made island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.62,Default,Ran,0,0,0,,These are the memories of "C"... So pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.60,Default,Ran,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:02.74,Default,December,0,0,0,,Don't go, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:09.02,Default,December,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ran... I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.24,Default,December,0,0,0,,Carly... Rogi... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:22.60,Default,December,0,0,0,,Ran's brain has been embedded with refined neurons,\Nsixteen times more than a normal person would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.20,Default,December,0,0,0,,Of course, such a thing is impossible for a live human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:32.76,Default,December,0,0,0,,So she was given a dead body, one that\Nmoved using the power of necromancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:39.78,Default,December,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong with a girl like that wanting to\Ndestroy the Demon District, the place where she was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.22,Default,December,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,, Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:49.54,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Maybe those kids have a valid reason for being angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:55.98,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Maybe Senga was right, and this island might\Ncause a large number of people to be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:18:01.58,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,But just as you guys want to destroy Itogami Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:06.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I, too, want to protect the people who live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:11.38,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So I'm going to stop all of you! Tartaros Lapus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:15.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,From now on, this is my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.84,Default,December,0,0,0,,I refuse to accept that kind of logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.16,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:27.40,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,W-We're here too, okay? For what it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.24,Default,Grenda,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.56,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's over,December!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.84,Default,December,0,0,0,,Not yet, Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:40.02,Default,December,0,0,0,,Appear swiftly! Dabih-Crystallus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:46.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,One of the Fourth Primogenitor's familiars, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.54,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,We should have realized earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:58.14,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,December... was the tenth month of the ancient Roman calender.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.98,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,The Tenth Kaleid Blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:06.76,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You're a seal for the Fourth Primogenitor's power,\Njust like Avrora was. Right, December!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:10.70,Default,December,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... Did you remember, Akatsuki Kojou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:11.98,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:15.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The Scorched Banquet that happened nine months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:19.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,And Avrora... I remember her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.90,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You... weren't involved in that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:28.06,Default,December,0,0,0,,I was the Third Primogenitor's captive back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.22,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The Third...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You mean Chaos Bride!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.76,Default,December,0,0,0,,It seems she's very interested in you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:40.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,I was only released because I told her that I wanted to go to Itogami Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.06,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You... Your body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:49.44,Default,December,0,0,0,,We, the Numbered, are literally the Fourth Primogenitor's seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:53.62,Default,December,0,0,0,,Once the seal is undone, we have no option but to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:59.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,The Tenth Familiar that was sealed within me, which is basically my own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:04.90,Default,December,0,0,0,,Dabih-Crystallus is a being that governs over the vampiric ability to charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.78,Default,December,0,0,0,,So we can even do things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:15.42,Default,December,0,0,0,,Even if the Rose falls, the Four Heavenly Beasts that were summoned will remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:20.32,Default,December,0,0,0,,The power to destroy Itogami Island, which was summoned by my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Dammit, come out! Natra-Cinereus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.38,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Rozenkavalier Plus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out, Al-Nasl-Minium!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.36,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Al-Meissa-Mercury!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:59.78,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I, Akatsuki Kojou, successor to the blood of "Kaleid Blood",\Nnow release your constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:06.86,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I, Sword Shaman of the High God and priestess of the Lion, beseech thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:14.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Dawn light of exorcism, spirit wolf of snowy mist, grant me the divine might of thy steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,that I may smite a hundred evil spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.84,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out, Fifth Familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.86,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Regulus-Aurum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.82,Default,December,0,0,0,,It's your win, Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:46.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,December!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.64,Default,December,0,0,0,,I have one last request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:57.14,Default,December,0,0,0,,Take Ran... Carly, and Rogi to a proper research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:01.44,Default,December,0,0,0,,The way they are now, they won't live for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.00,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.48,Default,December,0,0,0,,Thank you, Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.96,Default,December,0,0,0,,I'll give you the power of the Tenth Familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:13.26,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Wait, December! I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:16.44,Default,December,0,0,0,,Don't look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:21.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,It's fine. I will always be at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:32.12,Default,December,0,0,0,,Protect the Twelfth, Avrora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:36.78,Default,December,0,0,0,,That child is your hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,December,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.16,0:24:23.58,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,So you disappeared, December.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.22,0:24:27.80,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Worry not. I will take care of this island-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.80,0:24:31.72,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,You want to destroy the keystone and cause the island to collapse?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.54,0:24:35.30,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,I won't let you do that, Senga Takehito.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.90,0:24:39.26,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you still alive, Yaze Akishige!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:43.58,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Hyper Adapter!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:48.00,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,Sealing off Itogami Island, throwing the Island Administration into chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.16,0:24:52.40,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,And now, the Priestess of Cain has entered the casket.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.88,0:24:55.88,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,With this, all the preparations have been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.32,0:25:00.86,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,You have done well, Tartaros Lapus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.86,0:25:05.48,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,You were using us from the start...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.64,0:25:12.52,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,You're willing to go so far to slaughter the demons!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.94,0:25:15.16,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Descendants of the Sinful God....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.54,0:25:22.94,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,This can't be real... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.86,0:25:27.16,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,This is "C"? Cain's Coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.42,0:25:32.66,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Mogwai.... You are...!
